author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Concrete slab prep tips…I need to block off this area to pour new concrete. The 2x4 is level but I have a gap between it and the existing slab. I use @greatstufffoam Gaps and Cracks to fill that area and lightly spray it with water to speed up the cure time. This allows me to add the new concrete without any spillover to the other room. Many thanks to Great Stuff for sponsoring this tutorial 🔥#concreterepair #greatstufffoam #bathroomremodel #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
